<br>
Major Nuke Upgrades<br>
Good Pet upgrades<br>
Good Burnout upgrade<br>
Suspend companion<br>
<br>
Possible equipment upgrades:<br>
Focus items - Stack with nuke upgrades.<br>
Flowing Thought - Compounded with nuke upgrades and with focus item upgrades.<br>
Pet Focus items - Compounded with pet upgrades but not previous focus items.<br>
Horse - Compounded with nuke upgrades and focus item upgrades, stacks with FT upgrades.<br>
+Mana, +int - stack with nuke upgrades<br>
Click effects - dunno if there are any, but clicks are hard to evaluate until you get them.<br>
<br>
<br>
